title: Subgraph of pango XZ/XAC/XAD/XAE/XAP: (97 samples, 97 shown)
preamble:
A classic nested set of Pango X designations. The two XAD samples are probably wrongly separated here: it would be more parsimonious to group them which could remove 4 recurrent mutations.

See GitHub sc2ts-paper issue #339
